# Speakeasy-generated SDK — formatting is owned by `speakeasy run`, not prettier.
# Any prettier reformat here is overwritten on the next regen.
# (Use a `**` glob, not `packages/creem-sdk/`, so the openapi.json exception
# below can re-include the spec — gitignore rules can't re-include files inside
# an excluded directory.)
packages/creem-sdk/**
# Exception: the OpenAPI spec is the input to Speakeasy (we own it, not the
# generator), so it should be prettier-formatted for reviewable diffs.
!packages/creem-sdk/openapi.json

